text.tspan: Population whose cause of death is registered
The estimated share of people in each country whose cause of death is registered in the national vital registration
system. If all deaths were registered with a cause of death, the chart area would be full.
Data source: WHO, Global Health Observatory (2022); HYDE (2017); Gapminder (2022); UN (2022)
Note: Data points are taken as single-year observations between 2007 and 2016, depending on the country. The total number of deaths
is estimated using data from household surveys and censuses.
